meanings.definition: A genus of South American catfish in the family Trichomycteridae.
meanings.english_definition: A genus of South American catfish in the family Trichomycteridae.

etymology.value: From Ancient Greek 'κέρας' (kéras, "horn") + 'γλῶσσα' (glôssa, "tongue") + New Latin '-us' (forming nouns).
